HEADWORD: Osteodentine
<hw>Os`te*o*den"tine</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Osteo-</ets> + <ets>dentine</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Anat.)</fld>
